comments: Schroder (LAL) briefly places a hand on Murray (DEN) moving around the pick and the contact is marginal.
James (LAL) grazes Porter Jr.'s (DEN) elbow before making clean contact with the ball during the pass.
Davis (LAL) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Schroder (LAL) and Murray (DEN) mutually engage and immediately disengage during the rebound.
Porter Jr. (DEN) places his forearm to Davis's (LAL) front and initiates contact to his arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Schroder (LAL) brings his arm toward Murray's (DEN) path and marginal contact occurs during Murray's drive.
Davis (LAL) reaches in and initiates contact to Jokic's (DEN) arm which affects Jokic's SQBR.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in Schroder's (LAL) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
James (LAL) makes contact with the ball during Jokic's (DEN) upward shooting motion and dislodges it before incidental arm contact occurs.
Davis (LAL) contests the layup attempt and marginal contact occurs with Jokic's (DEN) wrist after the release.
Reaves (LAL) briefly places a hand on Jokic's (DEN) back as he turns into his shooting motion but immediately removes it.
James (LAL) and Gordon (DEN) make incidental contact with each other as both players pursue the rebound.
Brown (DEN) contests Reaves' (LAL) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Hachimura (LAL) briefly places a hand on Jokic's (DEN) hip as he posts up and the contact is marginal.
Davis (LAL) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Schroder (LAL) moves laterally into Murray's (DEN) body and initiates contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Schroder (LAL) establishes himself in Gordon's (DEN) path and marginal contact occurs to Gordon's side as he defends over the pick.
James (LAL) deflects the pass away from Jokic (DEN).
Gordon (DEN) retracts his hand against James's (LAL) body as he legally contests the shot attempt at the basket.
Reaves (LAL) commits a take foul on Murray (DEN).
James (LAL) gathers the ball and takes three steps to the basket.
Murray (DEN) reaches in and avoids initiating any illegal contact with James (LAL) during his drive.
Hachimura (LAL) commits a take foul on Murray (DEN).
Murray (DEN) absorbs the body contact initiated by Reaves (LAL) while contesting his driving shot attempt.
Reaves (LAL) commits a take foul on Murray (DEN).
Brown (DEN) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from James (LAL) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
